{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840252031,"sessionID":"ses_287ad6a83ffeH4bz0BkZUU7UOn","part":{"id":"prt_d7852a8cb0010st8s0ocIg55Mf","messageID":"msg_d78529669001aXQCKQ5y7CK2rX","sessionID":"ses_287ad6a83ffeH4bz0BkZUU7UOn","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_a4cf7f12076e4db68da893ff","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"Explore codebase for CRD patterns in agentcube project","description":"Explore agentcube CRD patterns","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project in /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure\n2. Existing CRD definitions in pkg/apis module - look for Go files that define Kubernetes CRD types\n3. The patterns used for CRD type definitions (e.g., struct definitions, webhook definitions, deepcopy methods, register functions)\n4. Any existing CodeInterpreter related code\n\nReturn:\n- Directory structure of pkg/apis\n- Example of existing CRD type definitions\n- Any existing CodeInterpreter types if found\n- How CRDs are typically organized in this project","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_287ad49e4ffeCpdwSWm1bWlCCY (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me provide a complete summary:\n\n## Summary: Agentcube Project Exploration\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/\n├── cli-toolkit/\n├── code-execution/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── deployment/\n├── idle-cleanup/\n├── integrations/\n├── pkg/\n│   └── apis/\n│       └── runtime/\n│           └── v1alpha1/\n│               ├── types.go         (Main CRD definitions)\n│               ├── register.go      (Type registration)\n│               ├── doc.go           (Package docs + group/version)\n│               ├── types_test.go    (Unit tests)\n│               └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go (Auto-generated)\n├── python-sdk/\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n├── session-routing/\n├── session-store/\n├── testing/\n├── go.mod\n├── go.sum\n├── design.md\n├── project.md\n├── proposal.md\n└── tasks.md\n```\n\n### 2. Directory Structure of pkg/apis\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                          # Package documentation with +groupName and +versionName\n        ├── register.go                     # Scheme registration functions\n        ├── types.go                        # CRD type definitions\n        ├── types_test.go                   # Unit tests for CRD types\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go        # Auto-generated deepcopy methods\n```\n\n### 3. Existing CRD Type Definitions (in types.go)\n\n**Two main CRDs defined:**\n\n1. **AgentRuntime** (short name: `ar`)\n   - Defines runtime configuration for agent sessions\n   - Fields: MaxSessionDuration, SessionTimeout, TargetPorts, PodTemplate\n\n2. **CodeInterpreter** (short name: `ci`)\n   - Defines code execution environment specifications\n   - Fields: AuthMode, MaxSessionDuration, SessionTimeout, Ports, Template, WarmPoolSize\n\n**Supporting types:**\n- `AgentRuntimeList` / `CodeInterpreterList` - List types\n- `AgentRuntimeSpec` / `CodeInterpreterSpec` - Desired state\n- `AgentRuntimeStatus` / `CodeInterpreterStatus` - Observed state\n- `TargetPort` - Port configuration\n- `PodTemplateSpec`, `PodSpec`, `ContainerSpec` - Kubernetes pod specs\n- `ContainerTemplateSpec` - Container template for CodeInterpreter\n- `AuthMode` - Enum type for authentication mode\n\n### 4. CRD Patterns Used\n\n**Kubebuilder Markers (in types.go):**\n```go\n// +genclient                           // Generate client\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true        // Is top-level resource\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status      // Enable status subresource\n// +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=ci   // Short name\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"  // Custom columns\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Required     // Required field\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Pattern=...  // Regex validation\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=...     // Enum validation\n// +kubebuilder:default:=...            // Default value\n// +optional                            // Optional field\n```\n\n**Register Pattern (register.go):**\n```go\nconst (\n    GroupName = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n    Version   = \"v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nvar (\n    SchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: GroupName, Version: Version}\n    SchemeBuilder = runtime.NewSchemeBuilder(AddKnownTypes)\n    AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n\nfunc AddKnownTypes(scheme *runtime.Scheme) error {\n    scheme.AddKnownTypes(SchemeGroupVersion,\n        &AgentRuntime{},\n        &AgentRuntimeList{},\n        &CodeInterpreter{},\n        &CodeInterpreterList{},\n    )\n    metav1.AddToGroupVersion(scheme, SchemeGroupVersion)\n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n**DeepCopy Methods (auto-generated in zz_generated.deepcopy.go):**\n- `DeepCopyInto(out *Type)` - Copies into existing object\n- `DeepCopy() *Type` - Creates new copy\n- `DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` - For runtime.Object interface\n\n### 5. CodeInterpreter Types Found\n\nThe CodeInterpreter CRD is fully defined with:\n\n**Type:** `CodeInterpreter`\n- Contains `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` (embedded)\n- `Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec`\n- `Status: CodeInterpreterStatus`\n\n**Spec:** `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n- `AuthMode` (optional, enum: picod/none, default: picod)\n- `MaxSessionDuration` (optional, pattern: `^(\\d+h)(\\d+m)?$`, default: \"8h\")\n- `SessionTimeout` (optional, pattern: `^(\\d+m)|(\\d+h)(\\d+m)?$`, default: \"15m\")\n- `Ports` (optional, array of TargetPort)\n- `Template` (required, ContainerTemplateSpec)\n- `WarmPoolSize` (optional, int32, default: 0)\n\n**Status:** `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n- `Conditions` (optional, array of metav1.Condition)\n- `ObservedGeneration` (optional, int64)\n- `Ready` (optional, bool)\n\n**Supporting Types:**\n- `ContainerTemplateSpec` - Image, Command, Args, Env, Resources, RuntimeClassName\n- `AuthMode` - string enum with constants `AuthModePicod` and `AuthModeNone`\n\n### 6. How CRDs are Organized\n\n1. **Single package approach:** All CRDs for a specific API group/version are in one package (`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n2. **Consistent patterns:**\n   - Each CRD has: Resource struct, List struct, Spec struct, Status struct\n   - Kubebuilder markers for code generation\n   - Auto-generated deepcopy methods (zz_generated.deepcopy.go)\n   - Registration in register.go\n   - Tests in types_test.go\n3. **API Group:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n4. **Version:** `v1alpha1`\n5. **No webhooks currently defined** (grep found no webhook definitions)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287ad49e4ffeCpdwSWm1bWlCCY","model":{"modelID":"MiniMax-M2.5","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube CRD patterns","time":{"start":1775840179736,"end":1775840252028}}}}
